            "description": "THE ROLE OF HR IN TRANSFORMING ORGANISATIONS \nHR is increasingly viewed as a strategic business function, and as such can play a key part in business transformations. This workshop will explore the role of HR in large-scale organisational transformations: \n\u2022 How data trends are changing the role of HR \n\u2022 How HR can play a more strategic role \n\u2022 Shift your \u201cwhy\u201d from a burning platform to burning ambitions \n\u2022 How to enable transformation through an agile mindset and culture \n\u2022 How to drive transformation through organisational capabilities"
